        "description": "Look up cached fare data for a specific route. Shows what fares are currently cached for a given origin-destination pair. Use when someone asks about 'fare cache', 'cached prices for JKT-SIN', 'what fares are cached', or 'demand cache by route'. Keywords: fare cache, route cache, cached fares.",
